28:06.918 --> 28:08.451
Virginia: - Good?
Jenny: - Yeah.

28:08.486 --> 28:09.853
Virginia: Thank you.

28:09.887 --> 28:13.256
Jenny: You have to get like...

28:13.291 --> 28:16.126
