28:36.080 --> 28:37.280
William: Nope.

28:37.315 --> 28:39.549
As you can see, I'm busy.

28:39.584 --> 28:42.018
Tessa: I started my period,
and I don't have any Kotex.

28:42.053 --> 28:45.121
I need to go into town.

28:45.156 --> 28:49.726
William: Well, uh, your mom
or-- or Libby can take you.

28:49.760 --> 28:50.927
I think that would be...

28:50.962 --> 28:52.028
Tessa: They're already in town.

28:52.063 --> 28:54.231
You're the only one
that can take me.

28:54.265 --> 28:55.932
William: [ Sighs ]

28:55.967 --> 28:58.401
Tessa: If you can't,
then you can't.

28:58.436 --> 29:00.337
