William: - [ Sighs ]

29:06.277 --> 29:08.144
[ Door closes ]

29:08.179 --> 29:10.881
[ Birds squawking ]

29:15.486 --> 29:19.089
You cannot hitchhike.

29:19.123 --> 29:22.993
You don't know the next driver
