29:23.027 --> 29:25.362
Tessa: Fine.

29:25.396 --> 29:27.931
I know you're busy,
so we can try the General Store.

29:27.965 --> 29:29.132
It's only halfway in.

29:29.166 --> 29:30.734
William: Fine.

29:33.170 --> 29:34.404
Tessa:
And you don't have to worry.

29:34.438 --> 29:35.705
I'm not going to ask you
about sex.

29:35.740 --> 29:38.375
William:
That... hadn't occurred to me.

29:38.409 --> 29:39.709
Tessa: No?

29:39.744 --> 29:42.045
I've heard Libby and mom saying
that I need a talking to

29:42.079 --> 29:44.281
from a strong, male,
authority-figure type.

29:44.315 --> 29:45.882
William: For God's sake, Tessa.

29:45.917 --> 29:48.551
Tessa: I'm on your side.

29:48.586 --> 29:50.720
We both agree
you are the last person on earth

29:50.755 --> 29:52.422
who should be talking to me
about sex.

29:52.456 --> 29:55.158
[ Radio turns on ]

29:55.192 --> 29:57.427
Cline: ♪ <i>just remember</i> ♪

29:57.461 --> 30:01.798
♪ <i>when a dream appears</i> ♪

30:01.832 --> 30:05.735
