like this.

30:22.820 --> 30:24.154
William: Your mother just wants
what's best for you.

30:24.188 --> 30:26.089
And as I am a gynecologist

30:26.124 --> 30:29.192
and I do talk to young women
every day...

30:29.227 --> 30:31.194
Tessa: You're really
a sex researcher.

30:31.229 --> 30:32.996
William: I am both, as you know.

30:33.030 --> 30:35.165
I am a doctor
and a sex researcher.

30:35.199 --> 30:36.533
Tessa: Along with my mother,

30:36.567 --> 30:38.602
who also calls herself
a sex researcher,

30:38.636 --> 30:40.570
and yet is too chicken
to talk to her own daughter

30:40.605 --> 30:42.873
about the thing she talks to
perfect strangers about all day.

30:42.907 --> 30:44.374
William:
And whose fault is that?

30:44.408 --> 30:46.243
If she were sitting here now
instead of me,

30:46.277 --> 30:48.712
you-- you would ignore
every word she said.

30:48.746 --> 30:51.982
And you wouldn't get the information
you so obviously need

30:52.016 --> 30:55.285
to grow into a safe,
responsible,

30:55.319 --> 30:58.855
sexually active adult.

30:58.890 --> 31:00.857
Tessa: You think I'm an adult?

31:00.892 --> 31:02.993
William: Hardly.

31:03.027 --> 31:08.231
Although you--
you will be soon enough, so...

31:08.266 --> 31:09.466
Just don't be foolish

31:09.500 --> 31:12.102
and ignore the advice
of people who know better

31:12.136 --> 31:15.138
and who actually care about you.

31:15.173 --> 31:16.773
[ Engine turns over ]

31:16.808 --> 31:18.041
Tessa: How about I trade you?

31:18.075 --> 31:20.277
You let me drive your MG
to the General Store,

31:20.311 --> 31:22.179
