to me about how my body works.

31:22.213 --> 31:23.713
William:
Oh, a perfect lose-lose for me.

31:23.748 --> 31:24.881
Tessa: So, do we have a deal?

31:24.916 --> 31:27.951
[ Both laugh ]

31:27.985 --> 31:29.886
[ Tires screech ]

31:29.921 --> 31:32.022
Virginia: I think Tessa's
been calling my mother.

31:32.056 --> 31:33.723
She hasn't said anything,
of course--

31:33.758 --> 31:34.858
