31:49.507 --> 31:51.141
Libby:
They would move to St. Louis?

31:51.175 --> 31:52.475
Virginia: [ Sighs ]

31:52.510 --> 31:53.677
Libby: I can't imagine
your parents moving anywhere.

31:53.711 --> 31:56.313
Virginia: Well, I can't imagine
