32:04.121 --> 32:06.423
Virginia: - Mm.
Libby: - And Henry and Tessa.

32:06.457 --> 32:07.624
I haven't seen Henry all day.

32:07.658 --> 32:09.626
Virginia: Well,
that's because he left the house

32:09.660 --> 32:11.428
and didn't tell anyone
where he was going.

32:11.462 --> 32:14.164
