32:14.198 --> 32:16.566
Libby:
Sitting on a bench with a girl.

32:16.601 --> 32:19.135
That the same girl
that crawled out the window?

32:19.170 --> 32:23.073
Virginia: That girl has clothes,
but, yes, that is the same girl.

32:23.107 --> 32:27.110
Henry... your ears
must be burning.

32:27.144 --> 32:28.178
Henry: Hey.

32:28.212 --> 32:32.249
Mom, Aunt Libby,
this is my friend Tina.

32:32.283 --> 32:34.951
Virginia: - Hello.
Tina: - Hello.

32:34.986 --> 32:37.120
Virginia: We shouldn't
have to chase you into town

32:37.154 --> 32:38.255
to meet your friends, Henry.

32:38.289 --> 32:39.556
They're welcome at the house.

32:39.590 --> 32:42.192
Oh, in fact, we are
just shopping for dinner now.

32:42.226 --> 32:43.894
Tina, would you like to join us?

32:43.928 --> 32:46.529
Tina: That's so nice of you,
but I-- I really can't.

32:46.564 --> 32:48.598
