if I'm gone too long.

32:50.501 --> 32:51.601
[ Chuckles ]

32:52.904 --> 32:56.373
Virginia: Of course he does.

32:56.407 --> 32:58.808
Tina: Anyway, um,
so nice to meet you both.

32:58.843 --> 33:00.076
Virginia: You, too.

33:02.613 --> 33:03.980
Henry:
I've got business in town,

33:04.015 --> 33:05.582
