33:05.616 --> 33:08.818
Virginia: What business?
You have to eat, Henry.

33:08.853 --> 33:10.120
Henry: I already ate.

33:10.154 --> 33:11.721
Libby: Why don't I go
and get started on the shopping?

33:11.756 --> 33:13.189
- Okay, Gin?
Virginia: - Okay.

33:15.226 --> 33:17.193
Henry: You can't guilt me
