33:28.572 --> 33:30.974
Look, you wanted me
to take charge of my life.

33:31.008 --> 33:32.242
I'm taking charge.

33:32.276 --> 33:33.910
You want me to show
some ambition and get a job?

33:33.945 --> 33:35.445
I am getting a job.

33:35.479 --> 33:38.548
I am buckling down,
as you like to say.

33:38.582 --> 33:40.216
I'll be home late.

33:40.251 --> 33:43.053
Virginia:
The kids will want you there.

33:43.087 --> 33:45.255
Henry: <i>You</i> want me there.

33:45.289 --> 33:46.756
Virginia: Henry, I insist.

33:46.791 --> 33:48.391
Henry: I'm almost 18, mom,

33:48.426 --> 33:51.061
so, honestly,
you insisting on anything...

33:51.095 --> 33:52.429
[ Horn honks ]

33:52.463 --> 33:54.831
Aah! Ugh!

33:54.865 --> 33:56.232
Virginia: Henry!

33:56.267 --> 33:57.534
Henry...

33:57.568 --> 33:58.935
Henry: - Christ.
Virginia: - Are you okay?

33:58.970 --> 34:00.537
Henry: - What an asshole.
Man: - I-I'm the asshole?

34:00.571 --> 34:02.072
- You didn't look.
Virginia: - Call an ambulance.

34:02.106 --> 34:03.206
Henry:
I don't need an ambulance.

34:03.240 --> 34:05.008
Libby: Oh, my God.
Oh, my God, you asshole!

34:05.042 --> 34:06.242
You absolutely need
an ambulance.

34:06.277 --> 34:08.545
Henry, do not--
Call an ambulance!

34:08.579 --> 34:10.045
Henry: Aunt Libby,
really, it's okay.

34:10.081 --> 34:11.681
Libby: It is not okay.
Do not goddamn move.

34:11.716 --> 34:13.516
Somebody call an ambulance!

34:13.551 --> 34:14.951
[ Breathing heavily ]

34:14.985 --> 34:16.286
[ Indistinct conversations ]

34:16.320 --> 34:17.387
Henry: [ Coughs ]

34:17.420 --> 34:18.722
Libby: No apology, no saying,

34:18.755 --> 34:20.023
"I'm so sorry
for nearly killing you."

34:20.056 --> 34:21.925
Henry: He didn't really
come close to killing me.

34:21.958 --> 34:23.560
Libby: You don't know that.

34:23.594 --> 34:25.395
Henry: I know my knee is scraped.
