34:25.429 --> 34:26.463
Libby:
You are not a doctor, Henry.

34:26.496 --> 34:27.864
Virginia: Libby...

34:27.898 --> 34:29.065
Why don't you go back to the
house and check on the kids?

34:29.100 --> 34:30.632
- George is on his way.
Libby: - Excuse me.

34:30.668 --> 34:33.937
I'm sorry, but this young man
was hit by a car,

34:33.971 --> 34:35.739
and we have been waiting
for nearly an hour

34:35.773 --> 34:36.873
for someone to see him.

34:36.907 --> 34:38.408
That is after
driving him here ourselves

34:38.442 --> 34:39.442
because an ambulance

34:39.476 --> 34:40.710
