to show up at the scene.

34:40.745 --> 34:42.478
Woman: We do apologize, ma'am,

34:42.513 --> 34:43.679
what with the long weekend
and all.

34:43.714 --> 34:44.880
Libby:
That's all you have to say?

34:44.915 --> 34:46.649
Virginia: Libby,
honestly, it's okay.

34:46.684 --> 34:48.618
Libby: It's not okay, Virginia.

34:48.652 --> 34:52.054
