your medical degree,

34:56.360 --> 34:58.261
your extensive knowledge
of internal injuries,

34:58.295 --> 35:01.731
that he may be bleeding inside
or have a-- a hematoma or a--

35:01.766 --> 35:02.899
Virginia: Libby--

35:02.933 --> 35:04.000
Libby: I don't know
what he has, either!

35:04.035 --> 35:06.436
All I know is that
Henry could have died!

35:06.470 --> 35:08.671
[ Sobs ]

35:08.706 --> 35:11.041
[ Birds chirping ]

35:16.313 --> 35:18.782
Virginia: The doctor's in
with Henry now.

35:18.816 --> 35:19.816
Libby: [ Crying ]

35:19.850 --> 35:21.151
Virginia: So far,
everything seems fine...

35:21.185 --> 35:24.421
