a thorough work-up.

35:27.358 --> 35:29.659
Libby:
I didn't mean what I said.

35:29.693 --> 35:31.961
I'm sorry.

35:34.698 --> 35:36.466
Virginia: Lib...

35:36.500 --> 35:39.402
